# AIRO — AI Resume Optimizer

## Environment Variables Configuration

Copy this file to `.env` in the root (for docker-compose) or into the respective `frontend/` and `backend/` directories.

### Backend Environment Variables (`backend/.env`)

```env
# MongoDB Connection
MONGO_URI=mongodb+srv://<user>:<password>@cluster0.mongodb.net/
DB_NAME=airo_db

# Security
JWT_SECRET_KEY=generate-a-long-random-string-here
JWT_ALGO=HS256

# AI / LLM (Groq)
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...

# External APIs
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...         # Required for contribution heatmap

# Email Service (SMTP)
MAIL_USERNAME=your-email@gmail.com
MAIL_PASSWORD=your-app-specific-password
MAIL_FROM=your-email@gmail.com
```

### Frontend Environment Variables (`frontend/.env.local`)

```env
# Backend API URL
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
```
